Hùynh Bảo Vi wrote a review Jan 2020
Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam7 contributions4 helpful votes
Recommend hotel
We were recommended to stay here by a friend. We booked a wrong room and the hotel was very helpful to help us to find the one we liked. The room was amazing, worth the extra money we paid! We had some annoying issues by staff then we gave our comments to the supervisor after trying so much not being picky. It was out of expectation that the hotel was full eared! Manager and his staff gave us a very sincere apology and made us feel comfortable with our choice. We keep recommending this hotel to whoever wants to stay close to the beach. In addition, it’s clean and new. Beautiful pool!
