Abader1973 wrote a review Dec 2019
120 contributions58 helpful votes
Reception not friendly and slow
Check out took 30 minutes. Allow for time delays if you have plane to catch. Hotel well located near beach. Nice roof bar and pool with views of the bay. Central location. Reception staff are extremely slow and not friendly.
Xin chào Abader1973, Warmest greetings from A La Carte Da Nang. First of all, thank you for choosing our hotel for your stay in Da Nang. We are very disappointed to learn that you did not like your stay with us. Your review is a big alert for us about the service quality, so we've conducted a deep investigation for this case. As double check the camera and room management system, from the time you arrived lobby until left was 27mins. However, upon your arrival at the lobby, your wife and son were still in the room which made us could not come to check the room and have to wait. Upon checking-out process, due to language barriers, we also took time to explain your son minibar consumption. Normally, it will take about 7-10mins to check-out a room, in your case, it took more time due to some objective reasons, we hope that you understand and await your sympathy. Any way,we are happy that you liked our location, view and great bar. Mr. Abader, every review is priceless for us and your review is a large alert for us to constantly improving. One again, thank you so much for your sharing and look forward to have another chance welcoming you again! Sincerely, A La Carte Da Nang Team
